    "2 The idea is then to scale exponentially the capabilities of a given AI system.",
    "In this sense, I will not discuss the possibility of theoretical physics to realize this idea but rather its philosophical implications and, specifcally, its moral implications.",
    "The Moral Landscape of General-Purpose Large Language Models Therefore, this chapter wishes to foster the development of Human-Centered Artifcial Intelligence (HCAI), understood as systems created by humans for humans, with the primary objective being enhancing human well-being.",
    "My analysis will therefore try to shed light on specifc issues related to General-Purpose Large Language Models, emphasizing ethical tensions and highlighting potential solutions to be explored.",
